<h4><span class="text-primary">CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS</span></h4>
<div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>

<p><strong>JURISDICTION: </strong>All matters directly and principally relating to amendments or revisions of the Constitution.</p><p><strong>CHAIRPERSON :</strong></p><img src='../members/images/18th/rodriguez-r.jpg' alt='Hon. Rodriguez, Rufus B.' title='Hon. Rodriguez, Rufus B.' 
        class='img-thumbnail img-responsive pull-left img-margin' width='145px' height='100px' /><h5><a href='../members/search.php?id=rodriguez-r' title='More info about our CHAIRPERSON'>Rodriguez, Rufus B.</a></h5><p>District Representative<br />Cagayan de Oro City, 2nd District<br /></p><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><p><strong>MEMBERS : </strong>55 Members</p><p><strong>COMMITTEE OFFICE : </strong></p><blockquote class='block-ital-sm'><p>3/F RVM Building, House of Representatives, Quezon City<br />Telephone no. 931-5001 local 7155, Telefax no. 931-3647<br />Committee Secretary: Ms. Aline Ruth V. Villaluz<br /></p></blockquote><p class="text-warning">SOURCE: Committee on Rules (Committee Membership) : BIS (Bills Referred) : Committee Affairs Department (Schedule of Meetings) : Engineering Division (Committees' Location/Telephone) : <abbr title="Information and Communication Technology Service">ICTS</abbr> (Website Maintenance)</p>
