  <h4>PRIMARY REFFERED HOUSE BILLS <small class="badge bg-badge-info">12</small></h4>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB00788</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB00788'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB00788.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-01</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE SELECTION OF AN ACTING PRESIDENT AND ACTING VICE PRESIDENT OF THE REPUBLIC OF THE PHILIPPINES IN CASE OF A FAILURE OF ELECTION</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=biazon-rr" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">BIAZON, ROZZANO RUFINO B.</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-23</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS since 2019-07-23</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB04062</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB04062'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB04062.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-08-20</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">AN ACT GIVING THE PRESIDENT THE POWER TO DELEGATE OR DESIGNATE A SUCCESSOR IN THE UNLIKELY EVENT THAT THE PRESIDENT, THE VICE PRESIDENT, THE SENATE PRESIDENT AND THE SPEAKER OF THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES DIE OR BECOME INCAPACITATED TO FILL IN THE ROLE OF THE PRESIDENT</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=castelo-p" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">CASTELO, PRECIOUS HIPOLITO</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-08-28</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS since 2019-08-28</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HCR0001</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HCR0001'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HCR0001.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-01</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">CONCURRENT RESOLUTION PROPOSING AMENDMENTS TO CERTAIN PROVISIONS OF THE 1987 CONSTITUTION OF THE REPUBLIC OF THE PHILIPPINES PARTICULARLY ON ARTICLES VI, X, XII, XIV AND XVI</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=rodriguez-r" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">RODRIGUEZ, RUFUS B.</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-23</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS since 2019-07-23</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HJR0003</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HJR0003'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HJR0003.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nb